@page "/"
@page "/Index"

<Title>Thin Blue Lie</Title>
<Meta Property="og:type" Content="website" />
<Meta Name="description" Content="Every year, police kill roughly 1,000 people and harass countless people, but much of it gets buried
    in documents and hidden from public view. Thin Blue Lie seeks to reveal this injustice." />

<style>
    .bluestrikethrough {
        z-index: 5;
        top: 1.5em;
        width: 100%;
        border: none;
        height: 3px;
        /* Set the hr color */
        color: #007bff; /* old IE */
        background-color: #007bff; /* Modern Browsers */
    }

    .header-image {
        display: flex;
    }

    .line {
        position: relative;
        width: 100%;
    }

    ul {
        list-style-type: none;
    }
</style>
<div class="header-image" style="background-image: url(Assets/Protests-Wallpaper.jpg) !important;">
    <div class="line"> <hr class="position-absolute bluestrikethrough"></div>
    <div style="flex-grow: 0; flex-shrink: 0; ">
        <h1 style="font-family: MillerItalic, Georgia, serif; font-size: 4em;" class="text-primary font-italic px-3">Thin Blue Lie </h1>
    </div>
    <div class="line"><hr class="position-absolute bluestrikethrough"></div>
</div>
<div class="container">
    <div class="py-3 px-5 border-bottom">
        <h6>
            Every year, police kill roughly <strong>1,200</strong> people and harass countless others. However, much of it gets buried
            in documents and hidden from public view. Thin Blue Lie aims to document and expose the widespread nature of police brutality
            in America by circumnavigating legal avenues to infromation, crowd sourcing all data.
        </h6>
    </div>
    <div class="d-flex justify-content-between mt-3">
        <div class="card mx-2">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title"><a href="/Events" class="text-black">Events</a></h5>
                <h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted">Access to our data</h6>
                <p class="card-text">Some quick example text to build on the card title and make up the bulk of the card's content.</p>
                <a href="/Events" class="card-link">Events</a>
                <a href="/Events" class="card-link">Submit Event</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card mx-2">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title"><a href="/Solutions" class="text-black">Solutions</a></h5>
                <h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted">Articles on Solutions</h6>
                <p class="card-text">We have written a series of essays on proposed and discussed topics.</p>
                <a href="/Solutions" class="card-link">Solutions</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card mx-2">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title"><a href="/Donate" class="text-black">Donate</a></h5>
                <h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted">Donate to Charities</h6>
                <p class="card-text">We have compiled a set of charites to donate to help the cause.</p>
                <a href="/Donate" class="card-link">Donate</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>


